    "body": "### Description\n\ntailwindcss lsp doesn't work well with tailwindcss v4 (removal of tailwind config file). I read this [issue](https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-intellisense/issues/1377) from their intellisense and tried to fix it in neovim with\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config('tailwindcss', {\n        settings = {\n          tailwindCSS = {\n            experimental = {\n              configFile = vim.fs.find(\n                { \"globals.css\" },\n                { path = vim.fs.joinpath(LazyVim.root.get(), \"packages/ui/src/styles\") }\n              ),\n            },\n          },\n        },\n      }\n)\n```\nbut the lsp.log gave me this message:\n```txt\n Invalid `experimental.configFile` configuration, not initializing\n```",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-31T21:20:44Z",
