        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The [error](https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-intellisense/blob/828e8e0bc03749797ca7ee6a493526146b82daa7/packages/tailwindcss-language-server/src/tw.ts#L315) I got is from LSP itself and not from neovim-lspconfig. the The field `experimental.configPath` does exist, it just the vim.fs.find() return an array `{\"path/to/the/global/css\"}` instead of just the string `\"path/to/the/global/css\"`. So the good config should be\n\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config('tailwindcss', {\n        settings = {\n          tailwindCSS = {\n            experimental = {\n              configFile = vim.fs.find(\n                { \"globals.css\" },\n                { path = vim.fs.joinpath(LazyVim.root.get(), \"packages/ui/src/styles\") }\n              )[1],\n            },\n          },\n        },\n      }\n)\n``` \n",
