        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "@CaoKha Could you please share the path of your config and structure of your project?\n\nBased on the information from this issue, the config might be:\n\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config('tailwindcss', {\n  settings = {\n    tailwindCSS = {\n      experimental = {\n        configFile = 'packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css', -- if cwd == monorepo root\n        -- or \n        --  configFile = 'src/styles/globals.css', -- if cwd == packages/ui\n      },\n    },\n  },\n})\n```",
